race.comment: NAZWAH (4) above average filly resuming. Lived up to expectations on debut when a sharp winner over 1100m at Gosford. Sent straight to the paddock when sixth over 1100m at Randwick last July. Impressed in her two trials and will take catching today. JUST AWESOME (2) speedy colt who knocked up late on resumption when third over 1100m at Gosford in fast time. Will slide across from the draw and give a ton of cheek. DIETRICH (8) consistent filly who gets map favours third-up. Comes out of a strong contest when third over 1000m at Gosford. Will go forward and sure to be thereabouts. MERCY ME (10) bounced off her good first-up second with a well-deserved Maiden win over 1100m at Gosford. Poorly drawn but can figure in the finish. AT HER MERCY (7) slick Maiden win second-up and stays in the mix.
